---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Testimonial Widgets for Social Media Managers | SocialProof" description="Freelance social media managers use SocialProof to collect client reviews and display them on their portfolio. Win more clients with real testimonials. Free to start." canonical="https://socialproof.dev/for/social-media-managers">
<style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; margin: 0; background: #fff; color: #111; }
    nav { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 1rem 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
    nav a.logo { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.25rem; color: #111; text-decoration: none; }
    nav .nav-links a { margin-left: 1.5rem; color: #555; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    nav .cta-nav { background: #111; color: #fff !important; padding: .45rem 1rem; border-radius: 6px; }
    .hero { text-align: center; padding: 4rem 2rem 2rem; max-width: 740px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .eyebrow { display: inline-block; background: #eff6ff; color: #2563eb; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .06em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: .35rem .75rem; border-radius: 99px; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15; margin: 0 0 1rem; }
    .hero h1 em { color: #2563eb; font-style: normal; }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.15rem; color: #444; max-width: 540px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; line-height: 1.6; }
    .hero-cta { display: inline-block; background: #2563eb; color: #fff; padding: .85rem 2rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem; }
    .hero-cta:hover { background: #1d4ed8; }
    .sub-cta { display: block; margin-top: .75rem; font-size: 0.85rem; color: #999; }
    section { max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 2rem; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
    .benefit-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .benefit-card { background: #fafafa; border: 1px solid #eee; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem; }
    .benefit-card .icon { font-size: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: .75rem; }
    .benefit-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 .5rem; }
    .benefit-card p { font-size: 0.92rem; color: #555; margin: 0; line-height: 1.5; }
    .quote-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .quote-card { background: #eff6ff; border: 1px solid #bfdbfe; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem; }
    .quote-card blockquote { margin: 0 0 1rem; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; font-style: italic; }
    .quote-card .author { font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; color: #2563eb; }
    .steps { list-style: none; margin: 0; padding: 0; counter-reset: steps; }
    .steps li { counter-increment: steps; display: flex; gap: 1.25rem; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 1.75rem; }
    .steps li::before { content: counter(steps); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; width: 2rem; height: 2rem; background: #2563eb; color: #fff; border-radius: 50%; font-weight: 800; font-size: 0.9rem; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: .1rem; }
    .steps li .step-body h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 .3rem; }
    .steps li .step-body p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #555; margin: 0; line-height: 1.5; }
    .use-cases { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; margin: 1.5rem 0; }
    .use-case { background: #eff6ff; border-radius: 8px; padding: 1rem; font-size: 0.92rem; color: #1e3a8a; font-weight: 500; text-align: center; }
    .bottom-cta { text-align: center; background: #2563eb; color: #fff; border-radius: 16px; padding: 3.5rem 2rem; margin: 3rem 0; }
    .bottom-cta h2 { color: #fff; margin-bottom: .75rem; }
    .bottom-cta p { color: #bfdbfe; margin: 0 auto 2rem; max-width: 480px; }
    .cta-btn { display: inline-block; background: #fff; color: #2563eb; padding: .9rem 2.25rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 800; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem; }
    footer { border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding: 2rem; text-align: center; color: #999; font-size: 0.85rem; }
    @media (max-width: 640px) { .benefit-grid, .quote-grid, .use-cases { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>
<nav>
  <a href="/" class="logo">SocialProof</a>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="/for/">Industries</a>
    <a href="/pricing">Pricing</a>
    <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="cta-nav">Try free</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
  <span class="eyebrow">For Social Media Managers</span>
  <h1>Win more clients with <em>proof you actually deliver</em></h1>
  <p>You build social proof for other businesses every day. It's time to build it for your own. SocialProof makes it easy to collect client testimonials and display them where they convert.</p>
  <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="hero-cta">Start collecting testimonials free</a>
  <span class="sub-cta">Free forever for 1 widget · No credit card needed</span>
</div>

<section>
  <h2>Why testimonials are your #1 sales tool</h2>
  <p style="color:#555; line-height:1.7; margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Social media management is a crowded market. Prospects can't evaluate your work by looking at a résumé or a credential. They can evaluate it by reading what your current clients say. A portfolio page packed with real client reviews is your most convincing sales pitch.</p>
  <div class="benefit-grid">
    <div class="benefit-card">
      <div class="icon">🏆</div>
      <h3>Stand out from other freelancers</h3>
      <p>Most freelancers have a LinkedIn profile and a rate card. A polished testimonial widget on your site makes you look like a seasoned professional, not a side hustle.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="benefit-card">
      <div class="icon">📈</div>
      <h3>Justify premium rates</h3>
      <p>Clients pay more when they're confident. Ten testimonials talking about ROI and growth make your retainer feel like a bargain, not an expense.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="benefit-card">
      <div class="icon">🔄</div>
      <h3>Works across niches</h3>
      <p>Whether you specialize in restaurants, e-commerce, fitness, or B2B — category-specific testimonials show prospects you understand their world.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="benefit-card">
      <div class="icon">⚡</div>
      <h3>Embed anywhere in minutes</h3>
      <p>Drop your widget on your portfolio page, Linktree, or proposal template. Everywhere a prospect might look, they see your proof.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Perfect for these types of SMM businesses</h2>
  <div class="use-cases">
    <div class="use-case">Freelance Social Media Manager</div>
    <div class="use-case">Social Media Agency</div>
    <div class="use-case">Content Creator / UGC</div>
    <div class="use-case">Community Manager</div>
    <div class="use-case">Paid Social Specialist</div>
    <div class="use-case">Brand Strategist</div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>What your clients might say about your work</h2>
  <div class="quote-grid">
    <div class="quote-card">
      <blockquote>"Our Instagram engagement went up 340% in two months. She completely transformed how we show up online. We get DMs from new customers every week now."</blockquote>
      <span class="author">— James R., restaurant owner</span>
    </div>
    <div class="quote-card">
      <blockquote>"We'd been posting randomly and getting nowhere. She built us a content strategy and handled everything. Our follower count doubled and sales followed."</blockquote>
      <span class="author">— Tanya H., e-commerce founder</span>
    </div>
    <div class="quote-card">
      <blockquote>"Professional, creative, and actually gets results. I've referred three other business owners to her. Worth every dollar of the retainer."</blockquote>
      <span class="author">— Carlos M., fitness studio owner</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#999;text-align:center;">Illustrative examples of the types of reviews your clients can share.</p>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Get set up in under 5 minutes</h2>
  <ol class="steps">
    <li>
      <div class="step-body">
        <h3>Sign up free</h3>
        <p>Create your SocialProof account — no credit card, no commitment.</p>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div class="step-body">
        <h3>Add your best client testimonials</h3>
        <p>Import from Google or paste in LinkedIn recommendations and emails. Use your best 5–10 to start.</p>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div class="step-body">
        <h3>Embed on your portfolio or proposal</h3>
        <p>One script tag. Drop it on your website, your Carrd, or anywhere clients look. Takes 30 seconds.</p>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div class="step-body">
        <h3>Collect reviews from every new client</h3>
        <p>Send your testimonial link at project completion. New reviews appear in your widget automatically.</p>
      </div>
    </li>
  </ol>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="bottom-cta">
    <h2>You build social proof for others — time to build it for yourself</h2>
    <p>Start free, add your best testimonials, and embed them on your portfolio today.</p>
    <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="cta-btn">Get started free →</a>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <p>© 2025 SocialProof · <a href="/privacy" style="color:#999">Privacy</a> · <a href="/terms" style="color:#999">Terms</a> · <a href="/for/" style="color:#999">All industries</a></p>
</footer>
</Base>
